Package: eigencore
Title: Certified Partial Spectral Computation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "brad@example.com")
  )
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad@example.com>
Description: Native-oriented foundations for certified partial eigenvalue and
    singular-value computation in R. The package provides operator, problem,
    planner, result, and certificate APIs that will host native iterative
    solvers for large dense, sparse, generalized, and matrix-free spectral
    problems.
